The New York Times Best Sellers: Fiction & Non-Fiction - April 10, 2016
Format: ePub

Overview: The New York Times Best Seller list is widely considered the preeminent list of best-selling books in the United States. It is published weekly in The New York Times Book Review magazine, which is published in the Sunday edition of The New York Times and as a stand-alone publication. The best-seller list has been ongoing since April 9, 1942.
